title: Libs Are Ruining Our Economy
description: Fellas discuss Biden's collapsing economy and walk through the Senate map before playing King of the Hill. Dr. Mehmet Oz joins the progrum for an interview about his race for Senate from Pennsylvania. And Kevin McLaughlin checks in with the latest from the Common Sense Leadership Fund.
